name: Vortex Sky: Space Rusher
description:
Hey! Get into this spaceship and show everyone, who's the best!

You seems to be the best pilot of the Galaxy Academy and you have to prove your piloting skills!
If you'll survive, of course.

Fly through the vortex with the insane speed. And take your reward!

This exam will definitely help you fight the enemy spaceships or complete the dangerous missions in galaxy wars. But first you have to survive.

Features:

- Super high speed vortex tunnel as a track
- Amazing levels
- Tons of the custom spaceships. Choose your favourite!
- Original voxel design
- Addictive gameplay
- Show everyone your incredible reaction skills!

Become the best star pilot and compete with your friends!
Enjoy!
